      <h4>&#x2758; The Client Brief</h4>
      <p>
        The brief was to conduct a usability review using various methods of usbility testing and analysis and data analysis, including performace and accessbility testing and analysis and to then produce a usability report that identified the shortfallls in usability and the proposed changes that Total Swimming could implement to improve the overal usability of the site.
      </p>
